\f0\b\fs52 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 Modular movie day night shop light transitions\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading80\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 \
To create a smooth visual transition when the mall shifts from day to night, your script needs to handle three distinct lighting phases: 
\f2\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 Business Hours (Day)
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 , 
\f2\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 Closing Time (Transition)
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 , and 
\f2\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 After Hours (Night)
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 .\
Because your camera is completely flat and perpendicular to the walls, you can achieve a highly realistic lighting shift using 
\f2\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 Image Mask Blending
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 . This technique avoids harsh, sudden cuts and creates a smooth, atmospheric sunset and shutdown sequence.\
\
\pard\pardeftab560\sa80\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs42 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 1. The Three Lighting Assets Needed\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading80\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 Instead of using a single background image, your artist will deliver 
\f2\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 two distinct background sheets
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774  and 
\f2\b \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 one lighting map
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774  designed to fit your real-world dimensions:\
\
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0\AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774\AppleTypeServicesF393216 \cf0 {\listtext	1.	}\AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 mall_structure_day.png \'96 Bright, ambient mall lighting with active interior shop illumination.\
\ls1\ilvl0\AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774\AppleTypeServicesF393216 {\listtext	2.	}\AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 mall_structure_night.png \'96 The same scene, but with the main ceiling grids turned off. Only overhead safety running lights and illuminated emergency exits remain active.\
\ls1\ilvl0\AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774\AppleTypeServicesF393216 {\listtext	3.	}\AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 guard_flashlight_mask.png \'96 A 1920x1080 transparent sheet containing a soft, semi-transparent white cone gradient. This represents the light beam cast from the guard\'92s hand.\
