\f0\b\fs42 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 2. The Timeline Trigger Logic\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading80\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 Using your 6-hour video timeline (648,000 frames total), we can divide the day/night cycle into four distinct operational shifts:\
\
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\f3\fs22 \AppleTypeServices \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f2\b\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 Frames 0 to 324,000 (Hours 0\'963): Day Shift.
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774  The mall is bright and open. Storefront advertisements are fully illuminated.\
\ls2\ilvl0
\f3\fs22 \AppleTypeServices {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f2\b\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 Frames 324,000 to 432,000 (Hours 3\'964): Closing Time.
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774  The sun begins to set. The script slowly dissolves the day background into the night background over the course of an hour.\
\ls2\ilvl0
\f3\fs22 \AppleTypeServices {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f2\b\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 Frames 432,000 to 540,000 (Hours 4\'965): Deep Night.
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774  The mall is closed and dark. The guard turns on his flashlight to illuminate the corridors.\
\ls2\ilvl0
\f3\fs22 \AppleTypeServices {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f2\b\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 Frames 540,000 to 648,000 (Hours 5\'966): Morning Sunrise.
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774  The dawn light slowly blends the bright daytime assets back into the scene.\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading80\partightenfactor0
\AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab560\sa80\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs42 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 3. Python Implementation: The Smooth Transition Engine\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading80\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 This logic replaces the basic image loading section inside your main loop. It calculates a frame-by-frame alpha blend value (
\fs28\fsmilli14118 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 blend_alpha
\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 ) to seamlessly transition between the daytime and nighttime artwork.\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading40\partightenfactor0

\f4\i\fs28\fsmilli14118 \AppleTypeServices \cf0 # --- ADVANCED DAY/NIGHT LIGHTING TRANSITION ENGINE ---
\f5\i0 \
\

\f4\i # Establish transition frame benchmarks based on the 6-hour timeline
\f5\i0 \
CROSSFADE_DURATION = 1 * 60 * 60 * FRAME_RATE 
\f4\i # 1 Hour transition phase (108,000 frames)
\f5\i0 \
CLOSING_START = 3 * 60 * 60 * FRAME_RATE      
\f4\i # Triggers at Hour 3
\f5\i0 \
SUNRISE_START = 5 * 60 * 60 * FRAME_RATE      
\f4\i # Triggers at Hour 5
\f5\i0 \
\

\f4\i # Initialize the canvas selection for this specific frame
\f5\i0 \
if CLOSING_START <= cycle_frame < (CLOSING_START + CROSSFADE_DURATION):\
    
\f4\i # PHASE 1: CLOSING TIME CROSSFADE (Day dissolves into Night)
\f5\i0 \
    
\f4\i # Calculate a value shifting from 0.0 (Pure Day) to 1.0 (Pure Night)
\f5\i0 \
    progress = (cycle_frame - CLOSING_START) / CROSSFADE_DURATION\
    canvas_base = Image.blend(bg_day, bg_night, alpha=progress)\
    is_mall_open = True if progress < 0.5 else False 
\f4\i # Shut down ads halfway through sunset
\f5\i0 \
\
elif SUNRISE_START <= cycle_frame < (SUNRISE_START + CROSSFADE_DURATION):\
    
\f4\i # PHASE 2: SUNRISE CROSSFADE (Night dissolves into Day)
\f5\i0 \
    
\f4\i # Calculate a value shifting from 0.0 (Pure Night) to 1.0 (Pure Day)
\f5\i0 \
    progress = (cycle_frame - SUNRISE_START) / CROSSFADE_DURATION\
    canvas_base = Image.blend(bg_night, bg_day, alpha=progress)\
    is_mall_open = True if progress > 0.5 else False\
\
elif (CLOSING_START + CROSSFADE_DURATION) <= cycle_frame < SUNRISE_START:\
    
\f4\i # PHASE 3: DEEP NIGHT OPERATIONS
\f5\i0 \
    canvas_base = bg_night.copy()\
    is_mall_open = False\
else:\
    
\f4\i # PHASE 4: STANDARD BRIGHT BUSINESS HOURS
\f5\i0 \
    canvas_base = bg_day.copy()\
    is_mall_open = True\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading80\partightenfactor0

