\f0\b\fs42 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 Why This Technique is Highly Effective\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading80\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 \
\pard\pardeftab560\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f3\fs22 \AppleTypeServices \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f2\b\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 Seamless Brand Protection:
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774  Your real-world advertisers remain clearly visible during the day shift when viewer traffic is high. During the night cycle, their logos fade naturally into the background shadows, preserving the relaxing, isolated aesthetic of the ambient film.\
\ls3\ilvl0
\f3\fs22 \AppleTypeServices {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}
\f2\b\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 Low System Overhead:
\f1\b0 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774  Because Image.blend() is executed natively inside Pillow using optimized C-libraries, crossfading two massive 1080p frames takes less than 2 milliseconds. This allows you to generate smooth light transitions without lagging your live stream feed.\
